<h1>Dropdown menus</h1>

<p>Clean and simple dropdown style menus for lists, or anything else.</p>

<h2>DropdownContainer</h2>

<p class="lead">A dropdown for displaying anything.</p>

<p>Use the <code>dropdown-container</code> tag to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/DropdownContainer.html">havok/widget/DropdownContainer</a> widget. An empty dropdown that can be filled with whatever content you choose.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <div class="dropdown clearfix">
        <dropdown-container class="docs-dropdown-example">
            <h5>Stuff here</h5>
            <p>This is stuff inside a dropdown</p>
        </dropdown-container>
    </div>
</div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set dropdownExample1 %}
<dropdown-container>
    <h5>Stuff here</h5>
    <p>This is stuff inside a dropdown</p>
</dropdown-container>{% endset %}{{dropdownExample1|e}}
</pre>

